      "writtenOn": "2020-08-19T22:41:30Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Vadim,\nIs the structure written in the helloworld_standard still recommende?\nhttps://source.chromium.org/chromium/infra/infra/+/master:go/src/go.chromium.org/luci/examples/appengine/helloworld_standard/\n\n`appengine/frontend/` ... app.yaml, routers for default service, cron.yaml, queue.yaml\n`appengine/backend/` ... for backend.\nsub packages for application logics.",
