      "message": "The directory name `cas/appengine` is generic. And we may have others GAE module e.g. API, backend.\nFWIU, we don\u0027t have strong motivation to keep everything in one directory `cas/appengine`.\n\nTakuto,\nDo you agree with having `cas/appengine/frontend`?",
